channel.title: [REQ] I need a Falador Chisel Buyer
channel.description:
I can't seem to find a buyer that buys chisels... I NEED ONE!
I'm not gonna say the reason but I need a bot that gets 27 chisels and stores them in the bank on each run.
This may seem like a "hobo that wants a tin hat" scenario, but I'm dead serious that I need this chisel buyer, but I can't say why. All I can say is me and 5 of my closest friends want it. WE NEED IT. Thank you to the person who takes on this programming venture. :D
